---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
		<style>
			.hero {
				text-align: center;
				padding: 4rem 2rem 3rem;
				max-width: 650px;
				margin: 0 auto;
			}
			.hero-avatar {
				width: 120px;
				height: 120px;
				border-radius: 50%;
				background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b35, #ff9f43);
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				font-size: 3.5rem;
				color: white;
				font-weight: 700;
				margin: 0 auto 2rem;
				box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.3);
			}
			.hero h1 {
				font-size: 2.2rem;
				color: #333;
				margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
				font-weight: 700;
			}
			.subtitle {
				font-size: 1.1rem;
				color: #ff6b35;
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
				font-weight: 500;
			}
			.intro {
				font-size: 1.05rem;
				line-height: 1.8;
				color: #555;
				text-align: left;
				background: white;
				padding: 2rem;
				border-radius: 16px;
				box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
				margin-top: 2rem;
			}
			.intro p {
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
			}
			.intro p:last-child {
				margin-bottom: 0;
			}
			.highlight {
				background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.1), rgba(255, 159, 67, 0.1));
				padding: 1.5rem;
				border-radius: 12px;
				border-left: 4px solid #ff6b35;
				margin: 2rem 0;
			}
			.highlight p {
				margin: 0;
				font-style: italic;
				color: #666;
			}
			.cta {
				margin-top: 2.5rem;
				display: flex;
				gap: 1rem;
				justify-content: center;
				flex-wrap: wrap;
			}
			.cta-btn {
				display: inline-flex;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 0.5rem;
				padding: 0.9rem 2rem;
				border-radius: 12px;
				text-decoration: none;
				font-weight: 600;
				font-size: 1rem;
				transition: all 0.3s;
			}
			.cta-btn-primary {
				background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b35, #ff9f43);
				color: white;
				box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.3);
			}
			.cta-btn-primary:hover {
				box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.4);
				transform: translateY(-2px);
			}
			.cta-btn-secondary {
				background: #f8f9fa;
				color: #333;
				border: 2px solid #e9ecef;
			}
			.cta-btn-secondary:hover {
				background: #e9ecef;
				transform: translateY(-1px);
			}
			
			@media (max-width: 720px) {
				.hero {
					padding: 3rem 1rem 2rem;
				}
				.hero-avatar {
					width: 100px;
					height: 100px;
					font-size: 2.8rem;
				}
				.hero h1 {
					font-size: 1.8rem;
				}
				.intro {
					padding: 1.5rem;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<div class="hero">
				<div class="hero-avatar">凳</div>
				<h1>👋 我是凳子大王</h1>
				<p class="subtitle">一切都有无限可能</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="intro">
				<p>
					不是什么技术大牛，就是个爱折腾的普通开发者。平时写写代码，踩踩坑，然后把踩坑的过程记下来。
				</p>
				<p>
					这里没有高深莫测的理论，只有实打实的实战经验。可能是某个框架的入门指南，也可能是某个 Bug 的解决过程，还可能是一些奇奇怪怪的技术探索。
				</p>
				<div class="highlight">
					<p>代码能跑就行，文章能看懂就好。</p>
				</div>
				<p>
					📍 随便看看 ↓
				</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="cta">
				<a href="/blog" class="cta-btn cta-btn-primary">
					📝 看看文章
				</a>
				<a href="/about" class="cta-btn cta-btn-secondary">
					🙋 关于我
				</a>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
